#LatteLook #LatteMakeup #sephoracollection #trendingmakeupartist

Missed our amazing conversation with @drgeetika yesterday? We’ve got you covered! Watch the highlights from our expert advice session on skincare with dermatologist, cosmetologist and founder of @isaacluxe, Dr. Geetika, and Sephora regional trainer, @kekuchina. Learn the secrets to hydrated, glowy summer skin.

P.S. - You NEED these products before stepping out under the sun! 🥰

✨The cult favourite @caudalie Beauty Elixir Face Mist contains plant extracts that tightens pores and smooths fine lines.

✨The @drdennisgross Alpha Beta Ultra Gentle Daily Peel Pad is a daily two-step peel that contains 3 to 7 acids and 12 anti-oxidants for exfoliation and protective hydration.

✨The @sephoracollection Matcha Sheet Mask has astringent properties known to control shine and purify skin.

✨Get yourself a @sephoracollection Quartz Roller for an at- home spa treatment that helps improve blood flow, reduces puffiness, and tightens the skin.

✨The @clarinsofficial Purifying Gentle Foaming Cleanser contains Alpine herbs sourced from their own farm, “Le Domaine Clarins”, and granules made with salicylic acid that gently washes away impurities, makeup, and pollution.

✨The best-selling @lancomeofficial Advanced Génifique Youth Activating Serum is a complex of 7 pre and probiotic fractions including yeast and bifidus extracts that helps to strengthen your skin’s barrier.

✨The @clinique Moisture Surge™️ 100H Auto-Replenishing Hydrator is a fan-favourite. With an Aloe Bioferment + HA complex and vitamins C and E, this oil-free gel-cream moisturiser penetrates deep and locks in moisture for an endlessly plump, dewy glow.

✨ @forestessentials’ Sun Fluid Tender Coconut Water is made from natural sun screen, tender coconut water, and contains sweet almond oil & virgin coconut oil.

✨The trending @wishfulskin  Thirst Trap Juice HA3 Peptide Serum has 3 types of Hyaluronic Acid (HA3) and firming peptides to hydrate and strengthen your skin.

✨The @sundayriley Good Genes All-In-One Lactic Acid Treatment is a lactic-acid, AHA serum that targets the look of pores, hyperpigmentation, and dark spots.

#skincare #summerskin #skincarelayering #activeingredients #dermatologist #sephoraworkshop
